description: "Gutfeld!" host Greg Gutfeld predicts the White House's latest move to issue corrections to a recent speech by President Biden could mean "we're seeing a shift" on Biden's candidacy.
title: GREG GUTFELD: White House staffers correcting Biden's speech might be a sign he is 'done'

description: One person is dead after a shooting outside of a Florida middle school award ceremony on Wednesday evening, the Marion County Sheriff's Office said.
title: Florida middle school shooting during awards ceremony leaves 1 dead; police say

description: Angelina Jolie was ordered by a judge to produce eight years of NDAs in the ongoing battle over Château Miraval in a legal saga with ex-husband Brad Pitt.
title: Angelina Jolie ally says Brad Pitt using winery case to 'punish her for leaving' as she's ordered to show NDAs

description: "Jesse Watters Primetime" host Jesse Watters describes how Democrats and elites' disgust towards populism is driving the weaponization of the judicial system against former President Trump.
title: JESSE WATTERS: Trump's visit to the South Bronx is driving the elites crazy

description: An American military hospital from World War I was dug up in France by archaeologists. Barracks, water pipes and several artifacts were discovered during the excavation.
title: American military hospital, dating back to World War I, uncovered by archaeologists in France

description: "The Ingraham Angle" host Laura Ingraham warned the "public has the right to know how radical" President Biden's judicial nominees are following a Senate Judiciary Committee hearing.
title: LAURA INGRAHAM: Democrats are 'doing everything possible' to control the nation's judiciary

description: According to the CDC, the second report of H5N1 bird flu in humans was reported in Michigan. The farm worker contracted conjunctivitis, or pink eye, but no respiratory infections.
title: Second American contracts bird flu tied to dairy cows as CDC says risk of infection still low

description: A cannabis policy researcher found that there are more daily marijuana users than there are Americans who drink alcohol everyday. Alcohol is still more widely-used than weed.
title: More Americans smoke marijuana daily than drink alcohol, study claims

description: Former FBI Director James Comey said the Biden Department of Justice had made a critical mistake while investigating former President Trump: It went too slowly.
title: James Comey slams Biden DOJ for moving too slowly on Trump investigation: 'We're stuck'

description: The CA Senate has approved legislation that would expand drug court programs, raise penalties for organized crime rings and close a legal loophole in order to make prosecuting auto thefts easier.
title: California advances legislation cracking down on stolen goods resellers and auto theft

description: The business and office of Hinds County District Attorney Jody Owens was raided by the FBI, although officials did not say whether the Mississippi prosecutor was suspected of wrongdoing.
title: FBI agents raided the office and business of a Mississippi prosecutor, but no one is saying why

description: The White House released its menu for Thursday's state dinner honoring Kenyan President William Ruto and his wife, Rachel Ruto, which includes lobster and short ribs.
title: White House reveals dinner menu for state dinner with Kenyan president

description: Only half the people in the U.S. feel they could be helpful in an emergency situation, according to the results of a new poll by The Ohio State University Wexner Medical Center.
title: Half of Americans not equipped to provide life-saving treatment in a crisis, poll finds
